<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="28Sep1938"><font color="red">28 September 1938</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): W.i.P. Send back sets of page proofs and the galleys I gave you on Sunday (25 September 1938) &hellip; Will correct them with Helen? &hellip; Please give my address to concierge and Galignani. </div>
